# Vendored W3C DPV release tree.
#
# Only the Turtle (.ttl) files actually consumed by scripts/dpv_to_linkml.py
# are tracked. All other serialisations (HTML, JSON-LD, N3, OMN, RDF/XML, CSV)
# carry the same information and are ignored to keep the repo small.
#
# Scripts that read from upstream-releases/:
#   - scripts/dpv_to_linkml.py
#       dpv/dpv/dpv-owl.ttl       (aggregate OWL ontology — identity)
#       dpv/dpv/dpv.ttl           (aggregate canonical/SKOS — enrichment)
#       dpv/dpv/modules/*-owl.ttl (per-module OWL ontology — identity)
#       dpv/dpv/modules/*.ttl     (per-module canonical/SKOS — enrichment)
#   - scripts/csv_to_sssom.py
#       mappings/<source>/dpv-<source>.csv   (kept as-is; sibling tree)
#   - scripts/gen_dpv_27560.py
#       ../schema/dpv-27560.ttl   (outside upstream-releases/)
#
# Ignore everything under dpv/ by default; re-include only the .ttl files
# that dpv_to_linkml.py reads. Re-inclusion requires un-ignoring each
# parent directory along the way (git won't recurse into an ignored dir).
dpv/*
!dpv/dpv
dpv/dpv/*
!dpv/dpv/dpv-owl.ttl
!dpv/dpv/dpv.ttl
!dpv/dpv/modules
dpv/dpv/modules/*
!dpv/dpv/modules/*.ttl
